Assistant: Absolutely! Here are some practical examples to help you out:

**Basic Svelte Component**:

```yaml
<script>
	function greet() {
		alert('Welcome to Svelte!');
	}
</script>

<button onclick={greet}>click me</button>

<style>
	button {
		font-size: 2em;
	}
</style>
```

